  "texts": [
    "If information was provided to identify a specific journal article, the Journal name/volume/issue/pages information was entered into the Google search window and the search was initiated.",
    "If this search strategy did not reveal the anticipated article, additional searches were attempted using Google Scholar and PubMed.",
    "When difficulties were encountered using information provided by students or ChatGPT-4o, Journal name/volume/issue/pages, information was used at the Journal website to attempt to authenticate the content appearing in the journal at the suggested destination by searching through the journal's archived material (if available).As a first round to evaluate the authenticity of references cited by students and Chat-GPT-4o, journals and online materials were queried via Google.",
    "Journals were further evaluated for current impact factor (IF) data using the online journal IF search engine, Bioxbio.",
    "All IF metrics were compared to Journal landing page information for concordance."
  ],
